"block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35117,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/01\/tuba-faults\/","url_meta":{"origin":33435,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Humility: Blessed is one busy with self-improvement","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 1, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBlessed is he who is occupied with his own faults over the faults of people.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Bazza\u0304r 6237 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0647 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645 \u0637\u064f\u0648\u0628\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38326,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/10\/07\/blessed-parents\/","url_meta":{"origin":33435,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Parents: Blessed is one who treats parents well","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 7, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Anas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBlessed is one who is good to his parents. Allah Almighty will extend his lifespan.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u030